Cycle Level Simulator - Project from Computer Architecture which includes a main program lc3bsim3 C source
	file, microcode (ucode3) as well as a control signal spreadsheet. The objective was to properly implement the full FSM of 
	the LC-3b using the datapath diagram, FSM path, and the microsequencer to establish what control signals needed to be on 
	corresponding to what state as well as determining the next state based on the microsequencer. 
